OL,3,CMichael Morpurgo says children learn
OL,4,Cbest by getting lost in a story
OL,6,FAuthor Sir Michael Morpurgo has
OL,7,Fchampioned reading and getting lost in
OL,8,Fa story as the best way for children
OL,9,Fto learn.
OL,11,FThe former children's laureate, 82,
OL,12,Fhas published a new original legend,
OL,13,FThe Miracle Dolphin Of Mevagissey,
OL,14,Fwhich is set in a Cornish harbour and
OL,15,Ffollows the life-saving bond between a
OL,16,Ffisherman's son and a dolphin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
