OL,3,CMichael Morpurgo says children learn
OL,4,Cbest by getting lost in a story
OL,6,FPublished on World Book Day, the story
OL,7,Fis part of a newly reissued collection
OL,8,Fof myths titled The Line To Legend
OL,9,FLand which features 11 classic legends
OL,10,Ffrom the South West and Wales.
OL,12,FMarking the launch of the new volume,
OL,13,Fpublished in partnership with Great
OL,14,FWestern Railway (GWR), five statues of
OL,15,Fsome of the featured legends,
OL,16,Fincluding the Red Dragon of Cardiff,
OL,17,Fthe Giants of Avon Gorge, and the
OL,18,FFaeries of Pennard Castle, will appear
OL,19,Facross a number of train stations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772679804
OL,3,CMichael Morpurgo says children learn
OL,4,Cbest by getting lost in a story
OL,6,FThe 5ft 8in statues will start off at
OL,7,FLondon Paddington, before travelling
OL,8,Fto Bristol Temple Meads, Cardiff
OL,9,FCentral, Swansea, Castle Cary, and St
OL,10,FIves to form the Legend Land Stories
OL,11,Fand Sculpture Trail.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the book launch, which
OL,14,Ftook place at Paddington station, Sir
OL,15,FMichael told the Press Association:
OL,16,F"GWR have done this wonderful thing of
OL,17,Ftrying to recreate the connection
OL,18,Fbetween books and children and reading
OL,19,Fand trains.
OL,21,F"I love the association.
OL,26,@xD@AOU}D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
