OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772679804
OL,3,CMichael Morpurgo says children learn
OL,4,Cbest by getting lost in a story
OL,6,F"I think one's got to remember that
OL,7,Freading doesn't belong just in the
OL,8,Fhome and just in the classroom."
OL,10,FSir Michael also said he does not
OL,11,Fthink blaming phones is the solution
OL,12,Fto get children reading again and that
OL,13,Fenergy should instead be spent
OL,14,Fencouraging them to read from a very
OL,15,Fyoung age.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
