OL,3,CMichael Morpurgo says children learn
OL,4,Cbest by getting lost in a story
OL,6,FThe new issue brings to life classic
OL,7,Flegends and follows a young wizard
OL,8,Fnamed Merlin, with each story retold
OL,9,Ffor a modern audience by
OL,10,FGloucestershire-based writer Brad
OL,11,FBrookes.
OL,13,FIt also marks 100 years since the
OL,14,Ffirst edition was first completed and
OL,15,Fincludes a personal introduction
OL,16,Fwritten by Sir Michael, whose books
OL,17,Finclude War Horse, Kensuke's Kingdom
OL,18,Fand Private Peaceful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
